Task
Is it true that the given word begins and ends with the letter `a`?
Create a variable str and assign it the value of an arbitrary string. 
Create an isCorrect variable and assign it a boolean expression that evaluates to true if the first and last letters of the string are a, or false otherwise.

Solution
const str = 'Abba'
const isCorrect = str[0] === 'a' && str[str.legth -1] === 'a';
